short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Block Blast Solver Pro is a tool that helps you solve Block Blast puzzles to get high scores.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Block Blast Solver is an unlimited online tool to help you solve Block Blast puzzles. It originated from the Reddit community and  can solve all 8x8 Block Blast puzzles. It supports game screenshot of IOS, Android and tablet devices.
